com.mindfusion.common

Class Duration

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mindfusion.common.Duration
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Comparable<Duration>

    public class Duration
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Duration>, java.lang.Cloneable
    Represents an immutable time interval.
